# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:18
translate spanish jez0_86979243:

    # "I am woken in the morning by a knock on my bedroom door."
    "Me despierta por la mañana un golpe en la puerta de mi dormitorio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:19
translate spanish jez0_caf3c8d0:

    # sp "[pcname]? There's a police officer here to talk to you."
    sp "[pcname]? Hay una agente de policía aquí para hablar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:20
translate spanish jez0_53533297:

    # "I bolt upright in bed. Police? I haven't done anything to warrant a police officer coming to get me!"
    "Me incorporo de un salto en la cama. ¿La policía? ¡No he hecho nada que justifique que una agente de policía venga a buscarme!"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:21
translate spanish jez0_d107d24a:

    # sp "She wants to ask you some questions about your father."
    sp "Quiere hacerte algunas preguntas sobre tu padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:22
translate spanish jez0_37fba660:

    # "Of course it's about dad. Stupid."
    "Claro, se trata de papá. Qué tonta."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:23
translate spanish jez0_2d0ea412:

    # pc "Okay, give me a couple minutes."
    pc "Vale, dame un par de minutos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:24
translate spanish jez0_3b51b7e8:

    # sp "Come down whenever you're ready. "
    sp "Baja cuando estés lista. "

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:25
translate spanish jez0_703b4584:

    # "I get up and quickly put on some clothes, go to the bathroom for my morning leak, straighten my hair, and brush my teeth."
    "Me levanto y me pongo algo de ropa rápidamente, voy al baño a hacer mis necesidades matutinas, me aliso el pelo y me cepillo los dientes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:26
translate spanish jez0_3dfa9768:

    # "Then, I take a deep breath and head downstairs."
    "Luego, respiro hondo y bajo las escaleras."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:29
translate spanish jez0_fa6b0e68:

    # "Lisa is sitting on the couch with another woman who's dressed in a sharp-looking suit."
    "Lisa está sentada en el sofá con otra mujer que lleva un traje muy elegante."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:30
translate spanish jez0_17b2e4ae:

    # "When she said a police officer was here, I hadn't expected somebody who looked like her."
    "Cuando dijo que había venido una agente de policía, no me esperaba a alguien con su aspecto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:31
translate spanish jez0_aee6944d:

    # "Woman" "We'll find something soon. There are just no leads right now."
    "Woman" "Encontraremos algo pronto. Es solo que ahora mismo no hay pistas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:32
translate spanish jez0_6a6053ec:

    # "Woman" "I'm sorry."
    "Woman" "Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:35
translate spanish jez0_bf6deed8:

    # sp "Oh, here's [pcname]."
    sp "Ah, aquí está [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:36
translate spanish jez0_5afbacaa:

    # sp "I'll let you two chat. I'll be in the kitchen if you need me."
    sp "Os dejo charlar. Estaré en la cocina si me necesitáis."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:39
translate spanish jez0_882032ff:

    # "[mom] gets up and walks past me, putting a hand on my shoulder as she passes. It's obvious that she's holding back tears. I guess the news is not good."
    "[mom] se levanta y pasa a mi lado, poniéndome una mano en el hombro al pasar. Es obvio que está conteniendo las lágrimas. Supongo que las noticias no son buenas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:40
translate spanish jez0_b7bdd522:

    # "The policewoman stands up from the couch and offers her hand."
    "La agente de policía se levanta del sofá y me tiende la mano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:41
translate spanish jez0_f3554eb2:

    # "Woman" "Hi, [pcname]. I'm Detective Rodriguez. I'm the lead investigator on your father's case."
    "Woman" "Hola, [pcname]. Soy la detective Rodríguez. Soy la investigadora principal del caso de tu padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:42
translate spanish jez0_37ae5b31:

    # "I shake her hand. Her grip is strong and despite her being a foot shorter than me, her posture and her eyes make me feel like I'm a child in front of her."
    "Le estrecho la mano. Su apretón es firme y, a pesar de que es treinta centímetros más baja que yo, su postura y su mirada me hacen sentir como si fuera un niño delante de ella."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:43
translate spanish jez0_bc87a0d4:

    # pc "Nice to meet you."
    pc "Encantado de conocerte."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:45
translate spanish jez0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_0_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_0_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:46
translate spanish jez0_ff6043ec:

    # det "Nice to meet you too. Why don't you have a seat so we can talk."
    det "Encantada de conocerte también. ¿Por qué no te sientas para que podamos hablar?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:49
translate spanish jez0_3da06234:

    # pc "Is everything okay? Did you find out anything about my dad?"
    pc "¿Va todo bien? ¿Ha averiguado algo sobre mi padre?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:50
translate spanish jez0_36c7f146:

    # det "Not yet. I'm just here to do a quick interview with you."
    det "Todavía no. Solo estoy aquí para hacerle una breve entrevista."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:51
translate spanish jez0_5a7bb805:

    # det "Do you mind if I record?"
    det "¿Le importa si lo grabo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:55
translate spanish jez0_0e24592a:

    # "She pulls a small voice recorder out of her pocket and puts it on the table in front of the couch, then switches it on."
    "Saca una pequeña grabadora de su bolsillo y la coloca sobre la mesa frente al sofá, luego la enciende."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:58
translate spanish jez0_df086b6b:

    # "She looks at me and raises an eyebrow."
    "Me mira y arquea una ceja."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:59
translate spanish jez0_c1a1605c:

    # det "Okay, if that's your choice."
    det "De acuerdo, si esa es su decisión."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:61
translate spanish jez0_cac288e4:

    # det "Did you have any questions for me before we get started?"
    det "¿Tienes alguna pregunta para mí antes de empezar?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:65
translate spanish questionsfirst_aee561dd:

    # det "Let me look."
    det "Déjame ver."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:67
translate spanish questionsfirst_73ed7052:

    # "She quickly flips through a small notepad."
    "Hojea rápidamente un pequeño bloc de notas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:68
translate spanish questionsfirst_fe578ae7:

    # det "We've talked to the two people he lived with - Lisa and Suzy."
    det "Hemos hablado con las dos personas con las que vivía: Lisa y Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:69
translate spanish questionsfirst_a76cc077:

    # pc "That's all?"
    pc "¿Eso es todo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:70
translate spanish questionsfirst_07673981:

    # det "From my notes, you are the only remaining family member, and you were out of the country."
    det "Según mis notas, tú eres el único familiar que queda, y estabas fuera del país."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:71
translate spanish questionsfirst_249eced2:

    # det "Previous wife died of cancer, both parents died of natural causes, no siblings."
    det "Su exmujer murió de cáncer, sus padres fallecieron por causas naturales, no tiene hermanos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:72
translate spanish questionsfirst_8ba569c2:

    # det "And it seems as if your father did not have very many friends. By all accounts he spent most of his time in the basement."
    det "Y parece que su padre no tenía muchos amigos. Según todos los indicios, pasaba la mayor parte del tiempo en el sótano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:74
translate spanish questionsfirst_e01c1bd1:

    # det "Is there anybody you can think of who we should talk to?"
    det "¿Se le ocurre alguien con quien deberíamos hablar?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:75
translate spanish questionsfirst_cc0ba283:

    # "I try to think of any of my dad's friends, but can't come up with anybody. He'd focused entirely on his work and me when I was growing up."
    "Intento pensar en algún amigo de mi padre, pero no se me ocurre nadie. Se centró por completo en su trabajo y en mí mientras crecía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:76
translate spanish questionsfirst_c60076a0:

    # pc "No, I guess not."
    pc "No, supongo que no."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:77
translate spanish questionsfirst_e7f6e1e8:

    # det "If you think of anybody, be sure to let me know."
    det "Si se te ocurre alguien, no dudes en decírmelo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:82
translate spanish questionsfirst_7f2eb30f:

    # det "My notes say that he worked from home doing some sort of computer programming from the basement."
    det "Según mis notas, trabajaba desde casa haciendo algún tipo de programación informática desde el sótano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:83
translate spanish questionsfirst_f286cc62:

    # pc "He was a quantum engineer."
    pc "Era ingeniero cuántico."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:85
translate spanish questionsfirst_83365159:

    # det "I'm not really sure what that is."
    det "No estoy muy seguro de lo que es eso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:86
translate spanish questionsfirst_499a2c32:

    # pc "It involves engineering on a quantum level. So, he wasn't a computer programmer, he was a scientist."
    pc "Implica ingeniería a nivel cuántico. Así que no era programador informático, era científico."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:87
translate spanish questionsfirst_c1c65336:

    # det "Okay, but he worked for PQ Technologies, right?"
    det "De acuerdo, pero trabajaba para PQ Technologies, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:88
translate spanish questionsfirst_43128ee3:

    # pc "Yes, he's been working for them for over 20 years."
    pc "Sí, lleva más de 20 años trabajando para ellos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:89
translate spanish questionsfirst_521e679d:

    # det "And he worked from home on his computer, correct?"
    det "Y trabajaba desde casa con su ordenador, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:90
translate spanish questionsfirst_10525e06:

    # pc "Yes. He had been working in their laboratory here in Skyhill, but when the lab closed five years ago, he began doing all his work remotely."
    pc "Sí. Había estado trabajando en su laboratorio aquí en Skyhill, pero cuando el laboratorio cerró hace cinco años, empezó a hacer todo su trabajo a distancia."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:92
translate spanish questionsfirst_1ff9fb4d:

    # det "Do you know anything about what kind of work he was doing?"
    det "¿Sabes algo sobre qué tipo de trabajo hacía?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:93
translate spanish questionsfirst_e2d71efb:

    # pc "Not really, no. Quantum engineering is all I know. He never really talked about his work."
    pc "La verdad es que no. Lo único que sé es que era ingeniería cuántica. Nunca hablaba de su trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:95
translate spanish questionsfirst_eb4656fe:

    # det "I see. Well, I talked to his supervisor and from what I can tell, the two did not really have a relationship."
    det "Ya veo. Bueno, he hablado con su supervisor y, por lo que sé, los dos no tenían realmente una relación."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:96
translate spanish questionsfirst_6c7e47a3:

    # det "Your father sent his work in weekly and the company paid his salary."
    det "Su padre enviaba su trabajo semanalmente y la empresa le pagaba el sueldo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:97
translate spanish questionsfirst_77d22bd2:

    # det "Everything was conducted through e-mail and there was no real contact."
    det "Todo se gestionaba por correo electrónico y no había contacto real."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:102
translate spanish questionsfirst_3eb51a74:

    # det "Our investigators looked through his car, which seems like it hadn't been driven in a long time."
    det "Nuestros investigadores registraron su coche, que parece que llevaba mucho tiempo sin conducirse."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:103
translate spanish questionsfirst_dd371cb0:

    # det "We could not find the keys for the car though. I assume he took them with him, wherever he went."
    det "Sin embargo, no pudimos encontrar las llaves del coche. Supongo que se las llevó consigo, dondequiera que fuera."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:104
translate spanish questionsfirst_4b3fad60:

    # det "We did a walk-through of the house and didn't see anything suspicious."
    det "Hicimos un recorrido por la casa y no vimos nada sospechoso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:105
translate spanish questionsfirst_9c61ea6b:

    # det "We went into the basement and looked through his equipment, but it seemed to all be work-related stuff down there."
    det "Bajamos al sótano y revisamos su equipo, pero todo lo que había allí parecía estar relacionado con el trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:106
translate spanish questionsfirst_9d03664e:

    # det "Our techs tried to gain access to his computer, but everything was password protected and encrypted."
    det "Nuestros técnicos intentaron acceder a su ordenador, pero todo estaba protegido con contraseña y encriptado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:107
translate spanish questionsfirst_a3576891:

    # det "From our investigation, it did not seem there were any clues to be gained by searching the house further."
    det "Según nuestra investigación, no parecía que se pudieran obtener más pistas registrando la casa más a fondo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:112
translate spanish questionsfirst_6f494b23:

    # "She looks up at me with compassionate eyes."
    "Ella me mira con ojos compasivos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:113
translate spanish questionsfirst_cb6742cd:

    # det "Oh no, I don't think so."
    det "Oh, no, no lo creo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:114
translate spanish questionsfirst_b700717e:

    # det "Statistics show that if a person is murdered, there's a 90 percent chance that it was a family member."
    det "Las estadísticas muestran que, si una persona es asesinada, hay un 90 % de probabilidades de que haya sido un familiar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:115
translate spanish questionsfirst_6d59f178:

    # det "Lisa seems to genuinely love him and I saw no history of domestic violence."
    det "Lisa parece quererlo de verdad y no vi ningún historial de violencia doméstica."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:116
translate spanish questionsfirst_92b418f1:

    # det "Same with Suzy. There didn't seem to be any malice there either."
    det "Lo mismo ocurre con Suzy. Tampoco parecía haber ninguna malicia por su parte."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:117
translate spanish questionsfirst_90d5bdd0:

    # det "And you were not even in the country, which seems to rule you out."
    det "Y tú ni siquiera estabas en el país, lo que parece descartarte."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:118
translate spanish questionsfirst_d744bb06:

    # det "The only other likely way he would have been murdered is if there was an intruder, which I saw no sign of."
    det "La única otra posibilidad de que lo hayan asesinado es que hubiera un intruso, pero no he visto ningún indicio de ello."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:119
translate spanish questionsfirst_96d6a9b3:

    # det "Or if he met somebody outside the house, which seems unlikely, as my information shows that he rarely went anywhere."
    det "O que se encontrara con alguien fuera de casa, lo cual parece poco probable, ya que según mi información rara vez salía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:120
translate spanish questionsfirst_57428a0d:

    # pc "I guess that makes sense. I can't think of any reason why anybody would want to kill him."
    pc "Supongo que tiene sentido. No se me ocurre ninguna razón por la que alguien quisiera matarlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:122
translate spanish questionsfirst_30ee331a:

    # det "Right. I'm not making any promises, but right now I don't think this looks like a murder case."
    det "Exacto. No te prometo nada, pero por ahora no creo que esto parezca un caso de asesinato."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:127
translate spanish questionsfirst_cf24e89c:

    # det "Honestly, no."
    det "Sinceramente, no."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:128
translate spanish questionsfirst_9c6a351f:

    # det "It looks like your dad just disappeared off the face of the Earth."
    det "Parece que tu padre simplemente se ha esfumado de la faz de la Tierra."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:129
translate spanish questionsfirst_2f75c2e8:

    # det "No traces of where he went, no suspects, no sightings."
    det "No hay rastros de adónde fue, ni sospechosos, ni avistamientos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:130
translate spanish questionsfirst_6896fafb:

    # det "It's rare that I see a case like this where we have zero clues whatsoever."
    det "Es raro que vea un caso como este en el que no tengamos ni una sola pista."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:131
translate spanish questionsfirst_2f418b2f:

    # det "But your dad was a very secretive person. We've had a hard time finding out what he was doing in that basement all day."
    det "Pero tu padre era una persona muy reservada. Nos ha costado mucho averiguar qué hacía en ese sótano todo el día."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:132
translate spanish questionsfirst_7c89a79a:

    # pc "He was just working down there, right?"
    pc "Solo estaba trabajando allí abajo, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:133
translate spanish questionsfirst_fc481599:

    # det "Maybe. But from what I can tell, he was down there all the time."
    det "Quizá. Pero por lo que sé, se pasaba todo el tiempo allí abajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:134
translate spanish questionsfirst_dc90f6b6:

    # pc "He was always very involved in his work."
    pc "Siempre estaba muy metido en su trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:135
translate spanish questionsfirst_211b9f32:

    # det "I've heard that, but usually when somebody is sinking themselves into their work like that, there are other factors involved."
    det "Ya lo he oído, pero normalmente, cuando alguien se sumerge así en su trabajo, hay otros factores de por medio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:136
translate spanish questionsfirst_64aa8452:

    # det "So while I have no real solid leads right now, I do have some suspicions."
    det "Así que, aunque ahora mismo no tengo pistas sólidas, sí que tengo algunas sospechas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:137
translate spanish questionsfirst_9958b44d:

    # pc "Which are?"
    pc "¿Cuáles son?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:138
translate spanish questionsfirst_dfb339ff:

    # det "I'm hesitant to tell you those until I am able to solidify them. And to do that, I need to ask you some questions as well."
    det "Prefiero no contártelas hasta que pueda concretarlas. Y para eso, también necesito hacerte algunas preguntas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:142
translate spanish questionsfirst_5a7a2301:

    # det "Okay then. I want to ask you some questions now."
    det "De acuerdo, entonces. Ahora quiero hacerte algunas preguntas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:144
translate spanish questionsfirst_98a0c1ad:

    # det "My information says that you have been away to college in Brazil for the last three years."
    det "Según mis datos, has estado estudiando en la universidad en Brasil durante los últimos tres años."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:145
translate spanish questionsfirst_36744f0b:

    # pc "That's correct."
    pc "Así es."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:147
translate spanish questionsfirst_9664f2b5:

    # det "Why Brazil?"
    det "¿Por qué Brasil?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:148
translate spanish questionsfirst_e69deced:

    # pc "It's one of the best colleges in the world for quantum physics, which was my major."
    pc "Es una de las mejores universidades del mundo en física cuántica, que era mi especialidad."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:150
translate spanish questionsfirst_8bf4ea8b:

    # det "So, you're a scientist, like your father?"
    det "Entonces, ¿eres científico, como tu padre?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:151
translate spanish questionsfirst_1509cdc6:

    # pc "He's an engineer, I'm more of a theoretical guy, but yes, we have a similar mindset and we studied similar things."
    pc "Él es ingeniero, yo soy más de teoría, pero sí, tenemos una mentalidad similar y estudiamos cosas parecidas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:152
translate spanish questionsfirst_58acd98d:

    # det "Do you know what he has been working on then?"
    det "¿Sabes en qué ha estado trabajando él entonces?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:153
translate spanish questionsfirst_52516e2f:

    # pc "No, we hadn't spoken in some time, and never about his work."
    pc "No, hacía tiempo que no hablábamos, y nunca sobre su trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:155
translate spanish questionsfirst_2db2eddc:

    # det "That's a little strange isn't it? You both study the same field, but don't talk about it?"
    det "Es un poco extraño, ¿no? ¿Los dos estudian el mismo campo, pero no hablan de ello?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:156
translate spanish questionsfirst_89bca239:

    # pc "He was always secretive about his work for PQ Tech. There were nondisclosure agreements involved."
    pc "Siempre fue muy reservado sobre su trabajo para PQ Tech. Había acuerdos de confidencialidad de por medio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:158
translate spanish questionsfirst_4339bc0f:

    # det "Were you angry at him for any reason?"
    det "¿Estabas enfadado con él por alguna razón?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:159
translate spanish questionsfirst_f3918cf6:

    # pc "I wouldn't say I was angry. We had some arguments before I left. It was all just teenage bullshit."
    pc "No diría que estaba enfadado. Tuvimos algunas discusiones antes de que me fuera. Todo eran tonterías de adolescentes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:160
translate spanish questionsfirst_1575bf56:

    # pc "I love my dad and I very much want to find him."
    pc "Quiero mucho a mi padre y tengo muchas ganas de encontrarlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:161
translate spanish questionsfirst_86a6f933:

    # det "When was the last time you spoke to him?"
    det "¿Cuándo fue la última vez que hablaste con él?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:162
translate spanish questionsfirst_5e38a5a3:

    # "I have to think about this one for a while."
    "Tengo que pensarlo un rato."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:163
translate spanish questionsfirst_9b9b3bf1:

    # pc "He called me on Christmas."
    pc "Me llamó en Navidad."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:165
translate spanish questionsfirst_bd00f9cb:

    # det "Christmas? That was nine months ago."
    det "¿En Navidad? Eso fue hace nueve meses."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:166
translate spanish questionsfirst_984bfd2a:

    # pc "Yeah. We didn't talk much for the three years I was away. My fault really. I never called him, and didn't make myself available to be called."
    pc "Sí. No hablamos mucho durante los tres años que estuve fuera. La culpa fue mía, en realidad. Nunca le llamé y no me hice disponible para que me llamara."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:168
translate spanish questionsfirst_e9703e8a:

    # det "So you really don't know anything, do you?"
    det "Así que realmente no sabes nada, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:169
translate spanish questionsfirst_26cc1233:

    # pc "No, I don't. I don't think I really even know my father that well."
    pc "No, no sé nada. Creo que ni siquiera conozco tan bien a mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:170
translate spanish questionsfirst_f6ae1ba3:

    # det "That's unfortunate. I was going to ask you some more questions, but I don't see how you're going to be able to help me with them."
    det "Es una pena. Iba a hacerte algunas preguntas más, pero no veo cómo vas a poder ayudarme con ellas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:172
translate spanish questionsfirst_1045479b:

    # det "I have them written down here and everything."
    det "Las tengo aquí escritas y todo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:173
translate spanish questionsfirst_4ccb6a12:

    # det "Do you know if your father was talking to other women?"
    det "¿Sabes si tu padre hablaba con otras mujeres?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:174
translate spanish questionsfirst_558d1253:

    # det "Do you know if your father was suicidal?"
    det "¿Sabes si tu padre tenía tendencias suicidas?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:175
translate spanish questionsfirst_c53bdc01:

    # det "Do you know if your father and Lisa are happy together?"
    det "¿Sabes si tu padre y Lisa son felices juntos?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:177
translate spanish questionsfirst_2c89c393:

    # pc "I don't know for sure on any of those things..."
    pc "No estoy segura de nada de eso..."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:178
translate spanish questionsfirst_f9fe0982:

    # pc "But from what I can tell and what I do know about my dad, I don't think he was talking to other women."
    pc "Pero por lo que puedo deducir y por lo que sé de mi padre, no creo que estuviera saliendo con otras mujeres."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:179
translate spanish questionsfirst_161fc62c:

    # pc "He always seemed happy with Lisa."
    pc "Siempre parecía feliz con Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:180
translate spanish questionsfirst_960826f0:

    # det "If you had to guess, what do you think happened to him?"
    det "Si tuvieras que adivinar, ¿qué crees que le pasó?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:181
translate spanish questionsfirst_8a4b7298:

    # pc "I really have no idea. None of it makes much sense."
    pc "La verdad es que no tengo ni idea. Nada de esto tiene mucho sentido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:182
translate spanish questionsfirst_19ea69da:

    # det "I'll agree on that one. This whole thing is really weird."
    det "Estoy de acuerdo en eso. Todo este asunto es realmente extraño."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:183
translate spanish questionsfirst_66d05663:

    # "I notice that throughout the interview Detective Rodriguez has gone from being a bit uptight and professional to now being much more familiar and personable."
    "Me he dado cuenta de que, a lo largo de la entrevista, la detective Rodríguez ha pasado de mostrarse un poco tensa y profesional a ser ahora mucho más cercana y afable."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:184
translate spanish questionsfirst_04fb76c2:

    # "She is talking to me more like a friend now than a suspect."
    "Ahora me habla más como a una amiga que como a una sospechosa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:185
translate spanish questionsfirst_20eb4f04:

    # det "Well, that's all I have for you right now."
    det "Bueno, eso es todo lo que tengo para ti por ahora."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:186
translate spanish questionsfirst_96541a04:

    # det "I'm going to keep looking into the case, but I'm sort of at the end of my rope here."
    det "Voy a seguir investigando el caso, pero estoy un poco al límite de mis fuerzas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:187
translate spanish questionsfirst_05821c09:

    # det "Plus, this is only one of the cases in the sea of different investigations that I'm currently drowning in."
    det "Además, este es solo uno de los casos entre el mar de investigaciones en las que me estoy ahogando actualmente."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:188
translate spanish questionsfirst_16709bfa:

    # det "I could really use some help here, if you could do some investigating on your own."
    det "Me vendría muy bien un poco de ayuda, si pudieras investigar por tu cuenta."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:189
translate spanish questionsfirst_12a0d1f6:

    # pc "Okay, what should I look for then?"
    pc "Vale, ¿qué debería buscar entonces?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:190
translate spanish questionsfirst_2da1948f:

    # det "Just anything that might tell us what your father was thinking in the days before he disappeared. Any journals or people who he may have talked to."
    det "Cualquier cosa que pueda indicarnos qué pensaba tu padre en los días previos a su desaparición. Cualquier diario o personas con las que pudiera haber hablado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:191
translate spanish questionsfirst_f59ecb78:

    # det "Maybe just ask around with people who might have known your father. A lot of times people will talk to the family more than they will the police."
    det "Quizá podrías preguntar a gente que pudiera haber conocido a tu padre. Muchas veces la gente habla más con la familia que con la policía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:192
translate spanish questionsfirst_51abcdfc:

    # det "Plus, when I get it approved, I'm going to unlock the basement for you. You could help out a lot by going down there and searching through your father's things for anything that might be useful."
    det "Además, cuando me lo aprueben, te voy a abrir el sótano. Podrías ayudar mucho bajando allí y rebuscando entre las cosas de tu padre en busca de cualquier cosa que pueda ser útil."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:193
translate spanish questionsfirst_76bc0e38:

    # det "My people don't know what half the stuff down there actually is."
    det "Mi gente no sabe qué es la mitad de las cosas que hay ahí abajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:194
translate spanish questionsfirst_1a8dbffe:

    # det "It's locked up as a crime scene right now, but I don't think that any crime took place down there and I should get approval soon to unlock it."
    det "Ahora mismo está cerrado por ser la escena de un crimen, pero no creo que se haya cometido ningún delito allí abajo y pronto debería obtener la autorización para abrirlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:195
translate spanish questionsfirst_35e6f7e9:

    # det "I'll let you know if I find any more information and you do the same."
    det "Te avisaré si encuentro más información y tú haz lo mismo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:197
translate spanish questionsfirst_d1abf90f:

    # "She hands me a business card with her phone number on it."
    "Me entrega una tarjeta de visita con su número de teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:198
translate spanish questionsfirst_75c93614:

    # det "That will get you directly to my cell phone. Any time, day or night, if you find anything of use, call that number. Got it?"
    det "Así me llamarás directamente al móvil. A cualquier hora, de día o de noche, si encuentras algo útil, llama a ese número. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:201
translate spanish questionsfirst_f9be908f:

    # pc "Got it. Thank you."
    pc "Entendido. Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:204
translate spanish questionsfirst_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_0_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_0_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:205
translate spanish questionsfirst_12498a38:

    # det "We'll find him, okay?"
    det "Lo encontraremos, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:206
translate spanish questionsfirst_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:207
translate spanish questionsfirst_a6c72070:

    # det "Tell Lisa that I said goodbye, will you? I need to go."
    det "Dile a Lisa que le digo adiós, ¿quieres? Tengo que irme."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:208
translate spanish questionsfirst_63023601_1:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:210
translate spanish questionsfirst_8ccade37:

    # "I walk her to the door, and she heads out to her car, starts it up and drives away."
    "La acompaño hasta la puerta, y ella se dirige a su coche, lo arranca y se marcha."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:212
translate spanish questionsfirst_cf442e3d:

    # "I glance over at the basement. I really want to see what is down there."
    "Echo un vistazo al sótano. Tengo muchas ganas de ver qué hay ahí abajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:213
translate spanish questionsfirst_0166920f:

    # "But for now, I guess I still need to wait. The detective has given me a lot to think about though."
    "Pero, por ahora, supongo que todavía tengo que esperar. Aunque la detective me ha dado mucho en qué pensar."

